## üì¶ Files & JSON Payload Examples

**`policy.json`**

```
{
  "name": "Example-Policy",
  "srcintf": [{"name": "any"}],
  "dstintf": [{"name": "any"}],
  "srcaddr": [{"name": "all"}],
  "dstaddr": [{"name": "all"}],
  "service": [{"name": "ALL"}],
  "action": "accept",
  "schedule": "always",
  "status": "enable",
  "logtraffic": "all",
  "comments": "created by API"
}
```

**`vip-update.json`**

```
{
  "portforward": "enable",
  "protocol": "tcp",
  "extport": "443",
  "mappedport": "443",
  "mappedip": [{"range": "10.146.42.239"}],
  "extintf": "any",
  "comment": "443 only"
}
```

